text: Harish Verma is an Indian actor who mostly works in Punjabi-language films. He made his debut in the 2010 film Panjaban, and gained wide attention with Yaar Annmulle (2011). He made his singing debut with the track Ikk Vaari Hor Soch Lae, which was written by Jaani and produced by B Praak == References == == Other Website == * * Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Indian movie actors
